<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/13531538-dearie"><img alt="Dearie: The Remarkable Life of Julia Child" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1344371053l/13531538._SX98_.jpg" />
